{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-152-writing-one-half-as-a-sum-of-inverse-squares","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 152: Izražavanje polovine kao zbir opštih kvadrata","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Postoje više načina da se napiše broj $\\frac{1}{2}$ kao zbir kvadrata različitih celih brojeva.</p>\n<p>Na primer, brojevi {2,3,4,5,7,12,15,20,28,35} mogu se koristiti:</p>\n<p>$$\\frac{1}{2} = \\frac{1}{2^2} + \\frac{1}{3^2} + \\frac{1}{4^2} + \\frac{1}{5^2} + \\frac{1}{7^2} + \\frac{1}{{12}^2} + \\frac{1}{{15}^2} + \\frac{1}{{20}^2} + \\frac{1}{{28}^2} + \\frac{1}{{35}^2}$$</p>\n<p>Zaista, koristeći samo potpune brojeve između 2 i 45 zajedno, postoji samo tri načina da se to učini; dva preostala načina su: {2,3,4,6,7,9,10,20,28,35,36,45} i {2,3,4,6,7,9,12,15,28,30,35,36,45}.</p>\n<p>Koliko načina postoji da se broj $\\frac{1}{2}$ napiše kao zbir kvadrata koristeći različite cele brojeve između 2 i 80?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4041000cf542c50ff17","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301783,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-152-writing-one-half-as-a-sum-of-inverse-squares"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function sumInverseSquares() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nsumInverseSquares();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>sumInverseSquares()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>301</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumInverseSquares(), 301);"}]}}},"pageCo